            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The flux-weighted average cross-section of the",
                " reaction 181Ta(g,n)180mTa was evaluated using the",
                " subtraction of experimentally determined",
                " cross-section of the reaction 181Ta(g,n)180gTa from",
                " the experimental cross-section of reaction",
                " 181Ta(g,n)180m+gTa estimated using experimental",
